BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:SLSF Phone Banks for the 2026 Midterm Elections
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260327T003000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260327T023000
UID:3816d78a55231ad2398ac7384c11082b@mobilize.us
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://mobilize-uploads-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/u
 ploads/event/Mobilize%20Events%20%281200%20-%20630%20px%29%20%2889%29_2026
 0128042619672529.png
DESCRIPTION:Join us along with the Bay Area Coalition to contact voters ab
 out the 2026 Midterm Elections. We'll be using the state-of-the-art autodi
 aler Scale To Win. We'll employ deep canvassing techniques such as active 
 listening to open our 2026 voter conversations and learn which issues are 
 important to them. No experience required - we will train you how to do ev
 erything. Thursdays from 5:30 - 7:30 PM (PT). If you haven’t heard of it
 \, Swing Left is a national network that helps people find high impact 
LOCATION:Virtual event
URL:https://www.mobilize.us/swingleft/event/893165/
X-SOURCE:Indivisible Sonoma County (Mobilize)
END:VEVENT
