 ploads/event/TrumpRegimeTakedown_Mobilize_20250829181612632740.png
DESCRIPTION:We do not consent to Trump and his billionaire allies taking a
  chainsaw to our government and our economy for their benefit! San Francis
 co is a sanctuary city and We the People need to defend the values that ma
 ke it so. Let’s stand united and oppose the endless assaults on our comm
 unities\, our civil rights\, the rule of law\, and our democracy. Keep dem
 ocracy alive every Saturday by showing up\, taking a stand\, and sticking 
 together for the long haul. Standing together is better than standing alon
 e
LOCATION:Corner of Van Ness and O'Farrell\, 999 Van Ness Ave\, San Francis
 co\, CA\, 94109
URL:https://www.mobilize.us/indivisible/event/835089/
X-SOURCE:Indivisible Sonoma County (Mobilize)
END:VEVENT
