BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Indivisible Sonoma County April General Meeting
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260414T010000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260414T030000
UID:d643afd4b69848d80412e52d7cf60e49@mobilize.us
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://mobilize-uploads-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/u
 ploads/event/Capitol%20cropped_20260320230559319502.jpg
DESCRIPTION:There are competitive primaries this year in two of the three 
 new congressional districts (CA-01 and CA-04) that fall within Sonoma Coun
 ty and Indivisible Sonoma County is working to endorse in each. As part of
  that effort\, we are reaching out to the four candidates and are hoping t
 o secure their participation in a candidate forum\, in person\, at our nex
 t general meeting. Following the meeting\, active Indivisible Sonoma Count
 y members* will be asked to take part in our endorsement vote. Stay tune
LOCATION:Finley Community Center: Santa Rosa Recreation & Parks\, 2060 W C
 ollege Ave\, Santa Rosa\, CA\, 95401
URL:https://www.mobilize.us/indivisiblesonomacounty/event/924951/
X-SOURCE:Indivisible Sonoma County (Mobilize)
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Indivisible Sonoma County Out-of-District Team
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260421T010000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260421T020000
UID:ba7e9e9d16dd9584eddaa78415badc23@mobilize.us
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://mobilize-uploads-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/u
 ploads/event/Turning%20Congress%20Blue_20260107203453834038.jpg
DESCRIPTION:The OOD group works to preserve blue and flip red seats. We've
  worked on both national and state races. We write postcards\, canvas\, te
 xt\, fundraise\, register voters\, phone banks\, research\, and coordinate
  with campaigns and political action groups. New members are always welcom
 e! Our get-togethers are informative meetings that discuss our plans to co
 ntinue holding the California districts we flipped in the last election\, 
 as well as to convert the remaining red districts in the upcoming election
 .
LOCATION:Virtual event
URL:https://www.mobilize.us/indivisiblesonomacounty/event/881687/
X-SOURCE:Indivisible Sonoma County (Mobilize)
END:VEVENT
